Editor's note: This livestream is expected to start at 19:00 CAT.  Livestream courtesy DStv 403, you can also watch it on DStv Now. JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa delivers the State of the Nation Address (Sona) in Cape Town on Friday night. This is for the first time Ramaphosa speaks as head of State. On Thursday, Ramaphosa was sworn in as South Africa's president following the resignation of ex-president Jacob Zuma. The address was postponed last week as negotiations to remove Jacob Zuma from the presidency played out. READ: LIST: Looking back at SONA 2017 top 5 memorable moments eNCA